room_title: Escape room "Case Closed" by Amazing Escape Room in Philadelphia
room_address: 101 N 15th Street, Second Floor Corner of 15th Street and Arch Street Philadelphia, PA 19102
room_description: One of the CIA operatives has just retrieved a classified document that could change the course of history. As a team of secret agents, it is your job to get to the secret safe house and locate the file, but beware of the authorities: they've already intercepted the message and will arrive in 60 minutes.
